# Dubai Metro MMS

Mileage Management System for Keolis MHI - Dubai Metro operator.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Start MongoDB
brew services start mongodb-community

# Seed database (first time)
cd packages/api && bun run seed

# Start API server (port 3001)
cd packages/api && bun run dev

# Start frontend (port 3000) - new terminal
cd apps/web && pnpm dev
```

## Stack

| Layer    | Technology                              |
| -------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Frontend | Astro 5.x + React 18 + Blueprint JS 6.x |
| Backend  | Hono + Bun                              |
| Database | MongoDB                                 |
| Solver   | Python + HiGHS MIP                      |

## Structure

```
uptime/
├── apps/
│   └── web/             # Astro + Blueprint frontend
├── packages/
│   ├── api/             # Hono API server
│   ├── solver/          # Python MIP solver
│   ├── db/              # MongoDB document client
│   └── types/           # Shared TypeScript types
└── docs/                # Documentation
```

## Python Solver

Uses [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) for Python tooling.

```bash
cd packages/solver

# Create virtual environment
uv venv

# Activate
source .venv/bin/activate

# Run tests
python -m pytest
```

